code: public Consumer createConsumer(Processor processor) throws Exception {     if (configuration.isPresenceAgent()) {         SipPresenceAgent answer = new SipPresenceAgent(this, processor, configuration).         configureConsumer(answer).         return answer.     } else {         SipSubscriber answer = new SipSubscriber(this, processor, configuration).         configureConsumer(answer).         return answer.     } }
public Producer createProducer() throws Exception {     return new SipPublisher(this, configuration). }
public void setConfiguration(SipConfiguration configuration) {     this.configuration = configuration. }
